    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? This car has been so good to me and it\u2019s still in really great shape! It runs smoothly, looks sharp, and is just waiting for a new home. I've taken care of it, and I'm sure you'll love how it drives. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice that\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend trips. Come check it out and take it for a spin\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
