    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This example features a 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring a pure analog driving experience. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system check and valve adjustment to maintain optimal timing and volumetric efficiency. The chassis retains its rigidity with a healthy subframe and refreshed bushings, providing the precise turn-in and lateral stability this platform is known for. Cosmetically honest with minor patina consistent with a well-loved driver, it is a turn-key performer for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 34500.0,
