      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a meticulously maintained vehicle that exemplifies consistent performance and structural integrity. This unit has been thoroughly vetted to ensure it meets our rigorous standards for mechanical reliability and aesthetic preservation. Offering a balanced synthesis of utility and value, this selection represents an exceptional opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-caliber vehicle that has been treated with professional care throughout its tenure.",
      "price": 29900.0,
