    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my car, and she\u2019s been such a reliable companion! It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been well-loved over the years. Whether you need a dependable daily driver or something for those fun weekend trips, this car is ready to go. I've taken great care of it, and it's got plenty of life left to offer. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love for you to come see it in person!",
