    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This Carrera 4S is powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six, featuring a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal to ensure long-term mechanical integrity. The drivetrain utilizes a precise 6-speed manual transmission paired with a viscous-coupling all-wheel-drive system for exceptional traction. Suspension performance is enhanced via Bilstein B16 coilovers, offering adjustable damping for superior turn-in and roll control. The braking system retains its factory-spec Brembo four-piston monobloc calipers and cross-drilled rotors, providing consistent bite and thermal resistance. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its mileage, the engine pulls strongly through the entire rev range with no bore scoring issues detected. A mechanically sorted example optimized for spirited driving.",
